            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> Iulio Pacatiano <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>gregio</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>proc</abbr><ex>uratori</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Augustorum nostrorum militiis <lb n="3"/>equestribus perfuncto <expan><abbr>proc</abbr><ex>uratori</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>provinc</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>O<supplied reason="lost">sr</supplied>hoenae praefecto legionis Parthi<lb break="no" n="5"/>cae <expan><abbr>pr<supplied reason="lost">o</supplied>c</abbr><ex>uratori</ex></expan> Alpium Co<surplus>ri</surplus>tt&amp;lt;i&amp;gt;arum adlecto <lb n="6"/>inter comit<supplied reason="lost">es A</supplied><expan><abbr>uggg</abbr><ex>ustorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>nn</am></abbr><ex>ostrorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>procurator</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>pro legato <expan><abbr>provinc</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> Mauretaniae Tingi<lb break="no" n="8"/>tanae col<supplied reason="lost">on</supplied>ia Aelia <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usta</ex></expan> Italica <lb n="9"/>p<supplied reason="lost">atr</supplied>ono merentissimo
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Inschrift wurde zusammen mit einer Bronzebüste gefunden. Datierung: Die Prokuratur des Geehrten in der Mauretania Tingitana fällt frühestens ins Jahr 197 oder 198 n. Chr.</p>
